            <title>[CAMEL-9666] Safe copy of DefaultExchange does not propagate &apos;fault&apos; property </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-9666</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;fault&lt;/tt&gt; property should be copied in the following places:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/camel-core/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/impl/DefaultExchange.java#L100&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/camel-core/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/impl/DefaultExchange.java#L100&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
