&lt;p&gt;Consequences:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;DefaultExchange#isFault()&lt;/tt&gt; does not work if &lt;tt&gt;exception&lt;/tt&gt; property is not set.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
